### ===========================================
### Security Demo — HTTP Tests
###
### REST Security with Elytron + @RolesAllowed
###
### Users (add with add-user.bat/sh -a):
###   alice / alice123  → role: user
###   bob   / bob123    → role: user, admin
###
### Authorization header = Base64("user:password")
###   alice:alice123 → YWxpY2U6YWxpY2UxMjM=
###   bob:bob123     → Ym9iOmJvYjEyMw==
### ===========================================

@host = http://localhost:8080
@app = security-demo

### ===========================================
### PUBLIC: No authentication required
### ===========================================

### Health check — @PermitAll, no auth needed
GET {{host}}/{{app}}/api/public
Accept: application/json

### ===========================================
### NO AUTH: Should return 401 Unauthorized
### ===========================================

### Secured endpoint without credentials — 401
GET {{host}}/{{app}}/api/secured/whoami
Accept: application/json

### ===========================================
### ALICE (role: user)
### ===========================================

### Who am I? — alice has role "user"
GET {{host}}/{{app}}/api/secured/whoami
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic YWxpY2U6YWxpY2UxMjM=

### User area — alice has "user" role → 200 OK
GET {{host}}/{{app}}/api/secured/user-area
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic YWxpY2U6YWxpY2UxMjM=

### Admin area — alice has NO "admin" role → 403 Forbidden
GET {{host}}/{{app}}/api/secured/admin-area
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic YWxpY2U6YWxpY2UxMjM=

### Dashboard — alice sees basic menu (no adminItems)
GET {{host}}/{{app}}/api/secured/dashboard
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic YWxpY2U6YWxpY2UxMjM=

### ===========================================
### BOB (role: user + admin)
### ===========================================

### Who am I? — bob has roles "user" and "admin"
GET {{host}}/{{app}}/api/secured/whoami
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic Ym9iOmJvYjEyMw==

### User area — bob has "user" role → 200 OK
GET {{host}}/{{app}}/api/secured/user-area
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic Ym9iOmJvYjEyMw==

### Admin area — bob has "admin" role → 200 OK
GET {{host}}/{{app}}/api/secured/admin-area
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic Ym9iOmJvYjEyMw==

### Dashboard — bob sees basic + admin menu items
GET {{host}}/{{app}}/api/secured/dashboard
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic Ym9iOmJvYjEyMw==

### ===========================================
### SPECIAL CASES
### ===========================================

### @DenyAll — always 403, even for admin
GET {{host}}/{{app}}/api/secured/maintenance
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic Ym9iOmJvYjEyMw==

### Wrong password — 401 Unauthorized
GET {{host}}/{{app}}/api/secured/whoami
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic YWxpY2U6d3JvbmctcGFzc3dvcmQ=
